{"tid":583083,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"疑似明目張膽賣翻版智能錶，近百人疑中伏","createTime":"2018-03-06T17:08:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T08:00:04.000Z","uid":96587,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"30494248ab4654883c024ba47ddff670bf62fade","tid":583083,"uid":96587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T17:08:17.000Z","msg":"Ticwatch 智能手錶官網價 $1249<br />\nFacebook page賣 $398，平成800蚊<br />\n<br />\n個page 得幾張相，&quot;本主页归属天津丰裕商贸有限公司所有&quot;，禁入個網仲係唔知咩文<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/010446_c14b66c3ac99bd328a5693aca2962f53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F010446_c14b66c3ac99bd328a5693aca2962f53.jpg&h=2151414a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPost link : <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/600249493699761/videos/163985497733607/?comment_id=794625157388845&amp;notif_id=1520341759024908&amp;notif_t=video_comment\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F600249493699761%2Fvideos%2F163985497733607%2F%3Fcomment_id%3D794625157388845%26notif_id%3D1520341759024908%26notif_t%3Dvideo_comment&d=UW%2F8ApER6lIp2DYUhoFWC54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=3d6fc86c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/600249493699761/videos/163985497733607/?comment_id=794625157388845&amp;notif_id=1520341759024908&amp;notif_t=video_comment</a><br />\n<br />\n有巴打去官方fb 查證<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/003819_f250e24c0dd8ac5ac18b696e73470aca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F003819_f250e24c0dd8ac5ac18b696e73470aca.jpg&h=d652d3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n官方fb 話假網，當然有機會因為官方覺得唔係自己官網，所以話係假網<br />\n而且就算個網假，都唔知隻錶係唔係真<br />\n<br />\n個位巴打po左張圖去個賣錶post 到，唔夠一陣就比人刪左<br />\n就連其他問詳細d 既巴打留言都刪埋<br />\n好似身有屎咁<br />\n<br />\n賣家話係正貨<br />\n但講到防水等級，一時就話係IP30, 一時就IP67 , 官方的係 IP67<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/005621_201346f1f494c6f5fac5ca5e3ff1b5bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F005621_201346f1f494c6f5fac5ca5e3ff1b5bf.jpg&h=dfae5c3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於NFC 功能，賣家話有NFC , 可以當八達通用<br />\n網上可以搵到，得大陸版先有NFC 功能，國際版係冇既<br />\n但賣家又堅稱係國際版<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/005800_1e4dcabb191d7ca3f0ab2e78964c23f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F005800_1e4dcabb191d7ca3f0ab2e78964c23f7.jpg&h=98618b7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本人的立場並不是指證佢地賣假野，只係對此有疑問，一齊討論下咁姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知大家點睇<br />\n<br />\n再利申: 本身已買一隻官方錶<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/010802_a4ca420bc67d6958121084acd0f950bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F010802_a4ca420bc67d6958121084acd0f950bb.jpg&h=7748d319&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf39039244cfb82017efae929db718f0c6d482c1","tid":583083,"uid":96587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T07:52:31.000Z","msg":"最新消息 ： 係假的<br />\n問左facebook已買的巴打<br />\n賣家最後比左隻雜牌<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1990903137830578/videos/141776753298363/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1990903137830578%2Fvideos%2F141776753298363%2F&d=UW%2F8ApER6lIp2DYUhoFWC54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=d1b0a7c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1990903137830578/videos/141776753298363/</a>"},{"pid":"555d295d130185fbfc7261d5f7cdddb44290f226","tid":583083,"uid":96587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T08:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/155953_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F155953_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=9c8bce8d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}